question: Match the nutrients given in List I with the source in List II:
List I: 1. Vitamin A, 2. Single cell protein, 3. Vitamin C, 4. Protein
List II: p. Bitter gourd, q. Beans, r. Carrots, s. Spirulina spp
explanation: Vitamin A is found in Carrots (1-r), Single cell protein is Spirulina (2-s), Vitamin C is in Bitter gourd (3-p), and Proteins are in Beans (4-q).
